<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="despite-prep">despite <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'spaɪt/    美 /dɪ'spaɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-in-spite-of">1.★ <strong>不管；尽管；任凭 (in spite of)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Joe is a good basketball player despite being short and stout.  
尽管又矮又胖，乔依然是个优秀的篮球运动员。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 1</footer></div>

<p>注: despite 与 in spite of 意思相同，但 despite 较文雅一些。  </p>
<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It is unbelievable that Mr. Lucas leads a simple life <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ his great wealth.  （2014 江西）<br />
A.without<br />
B.despite<br />
C.in<br />
D.to  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. B  </p></div>